d:</strong> McAfee\r\n<strong>Manufacturer Part #:</strong> MMSETD1RAA\r\n<strong>Our Part #:</strong> AVS-MMS-1Y1D\r\n<strong>Availability:</strong> In Stock\r\n<strong>Media Type:</strong> Download\r\n<strong>Platform:</strong> Android 8 or later','inherit','closed','closed','','90007233-revision-v1','','','2025-08-15 21:07:34','2025-08-15 21:07:34','',90007233,'https://staging-bf5f-antiviruspointorgdomainonly.wpcomstaging.com/?p=90008105',0,'revision','',0);
